              "text": "For the purposes of this section — “mining of digital assets” means the process by which digital assets are awarded for validating the state of the distributed ledger in the context of the distributed ledger’s consensus mechanism; “proprietary mining” refers to mining of digital assets on a person’s own behalf.",
