              "id": "sec14:p2",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "number": "(2)",
              "title": "",
              "text": "Where the Commission considers it necessary, it may establish and maintain a separate register for any digital asset business, and the provisions of subsection (1)(a) and (b) shall apply with necessary modifications.",
