                },
                {
                  "target": "first_schedule",
                  "text": "Form 7 as set out in the First Schedule",
                  "type": "internal"
                }
              ],
              "children": []
            },
            {
              "id": "sec17:p4",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "number": "(4)",
              "title": "",
              "text": "A registrant seeking to change or expand the scope of its activities shall submit a written plan describing the proposed materially new product, service, activity, or the proposed material change, including — (a) a detailed description of the business operations; (b) compliance policies; (c) the impact on the overall business of the registrant; and (d) such other information as requested by the Commission.",
