              "text": "Prior to a merger, acquisition or sale of all or a substantial part of the assets of a registrant, the registrant or its acquiring entity must submit a written plan of merger or acquisition that shall — (a) identify each entity to be merged, the surviving entity, or the entity acquiring all or substantially all of the assets of the registrant; (b) describe the terms and conditions of the merger or acquisition and the mode of carrying the merger or acquisition into effect; and (c) be in form and substance satisfactory to the Commission.",
