              "id": "sec23:p2",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "number": "(2)",
              "title": "",
              "text": "For the purposes of subsection (1)(a), the assets maintained by a registrant authorised to operate a digital asset exchange shall — (a) be beneficially owned by the registrant; and (b) be sufficiently liquid.",
